    ledgerPriceSkuStock###object 'Цена (базовая)' (sku, stock, object) = prevPricePriceListTypeSkuStockDateTime(ledgerPriceListTypePriceListType(priceListType###object###sku(object, sku)), sku, stock, dateTime###object(object));
